<L>__{exterior prison, digne night}
<A>__{he stops at the local jail. an iron chain attached to a bell hangs from the prison door. he rings. a grate slides open.}
<C>__{valjean}
<D>__{jailer. would you let me stay here for tonight?}
<C>__{jailer}
<D>__{this is a prison, not an inn. get yourself arrested. then we will open up for you.}
<A>__{the grate slides shut. as jean valjean walks away, some children who have been following begin throwing stones at him. he threatens them with his stick and they scatter.}
